{"tid":1241900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連狗有冇機會將621三罷post長期置頂","createTime":"2019-06-19T01:06:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T01:15:13.000Z","uid":94538,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7695fa117ad82416717c7de51f5cce91dda530a1","tid":1241900,"uid":94538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:06:47.000Z","msg":"身邊好多人都仲好緊張事態發展<br />\n唔知有幾多人好似我咁，對連登熱門F5上左癮<br />\n<br />\n但奈何今次發生太多支事件<br />\n令熱門啲post好散好亂...<br />\nFB都仲好多人keep住share post屌老母<br />\n但好重要既係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Next Step一啲都唔出</span></span><br />\n令大家覺得氣氛冇左<br />\n<br />\n而家定左620五點先決定621會否三罷<br />\n但而家個政府咁 希望大家都會預左要出黎<br />\n但發現身邊好多人都冇左呢個<span style=\"color: red;\">預左出既心態</span><br />\n什至唔知621行動<br />\n<br />\n612前一兩日<br />\nkeep住見到既係唔同公司、鋪頭、學校聯署一齊支持罷工罷課罷市<br />\n見到無限量既支持 氣氛係幾咁好<br />\n相信有一批人都係因為呢種熱血氣氛推左出黎<br />\n所以我地而家要既係621既<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">討論量</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我自己覺得第一步 將三罷呢個post真置頂已經幫到手<br />\n至少大家關心呢件事時都<span style=\"color: red;\">提醒自己621要Ready</span><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家討論，唔好淨係扔低一句氣氛冇左/預計621會失敗就算<br />\n<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1240180\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1240180</a>"},{"pid":"7fe5274fa919643c427da0027a13ec9357ae34ee","tid":1241900,"uid":94538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:08:15.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f53f238d0718973bb97ff6e3675b127bd3daeab8","tid":1241900,"uid":94538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:08:25.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d40ae89e571f879412a90d05c47284af3e58120c","tid":1241900,"uid":94538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:08:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\